    "notes": "Soccer v1.2.0 — Added VAR & penalty systems, dynamic weather & pitch wear, player attributes & progression, training drills endpoints, stadium/custom stadiums for clubs, expanded broadcast/camera director features, motion-captured special animations (headers/bicycle kicks), crossplay & ranked ladders, live-ops endpoints, photo mode & cinematic replay features, and enhanced accessibility options. Production: integrate live commentary feeds, streaming infra, persistent club backend, VAR decision authority server rules, and match integrity anti-cheat systems."
  }
}
